msg: Add security vulnerability database for httpd to the Apache site,
based on the database used by Apache Week.  The raw XML database of
vulnerabilities is marked up using XSLT into the XML used to build
the site.  This first commit adds the new pages but does not link
them into the site; making sure this all works as expected first before
removing the links to Apache Week.
